    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> I'd like to replace the facetName prop by a facet prop, with a name attribute but possibly other ones.\n\nIf your question comes from the fact that you are going to need to ask for a facetName <=> facetLabel/Title mapping in the upcoming clear-refinements proposal then I would say thats not a need we need to fill.\n\nThat's not a problem if one widget is asking for the facetName <=> facetLabel/Title mapping.\n",
